asset.hookText: It-model Cara Delevingne returns for the Fall 2013 season, this time opposite model Ollie Edwards, and special guest, NYC-based street artist, Curtis Kulig. All three were shot on location in various parts of New York City by renowned fashion photographer Mikael Jansson. Shop the Collection & Experience more of the Campaign at DKNY.COM.
